This program converts texts into Xiaofei Lu's LCA (Lu 2012) compliant data format. 
POS tagging is conducted with TReeTagger (Schmid 1994)

PREREQUISITE
Install TreeTagger

USAGE: Place all txt files in "corpus" directory and run. 
Command line in linux: perl runner.pl corpus

Run runner.pl. It encapsulates all other programs necessary for the preparation of txt files to be used in LCA. 

Text formatting path
txt 2 txtn 2 tokens 2 tt 2 seq4lca 2 seq4lca.


